<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٨٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6106">‌مُسْلِمُ بْنُ إِبْرَاهِيمَ، </a>نَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6685">‌هِشَامٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">‌قَتَادَةَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">‌أَنَسٍ </a>: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ صَلَّى اللهُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٨٥⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ وَأَبَا بَكْرٍ وَعُمَرَ وَعُثْمَانَ كَانُوا يَفْتَتِحُونَ الْقِرَاءَةَ:</span> بِـ <span class="c3">{الْحَمْدُ لِلهِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِينَ}</span>».<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>